  "img": "icons/commodities/gems/pearl-purple-dark.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">這個觸感寒冷，直徑</span><span class=\"1\">6</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">寸的深黑色球體可以召來夜晚。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">你可以花費</span><span class=\"1\">10</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">分鐘啟用它，一旦被啟用，則周圍半徑十里的區域都將被夜幕籠罩，不論將其啟用的時間點是白晝還是黑夜。黑夜將持續</span><span class=\"1\">24</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">小時，直到你與珍珠失去同調，或你使用一個動作終止此魔法效應。夜幕珍珠一旦被使用，則在接下來的</span><span class=\"1\">24</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">小時中無法被再次啟用。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></p></div>",
